formThreeBId.notesToCertificate: We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction cost.The preparation of the accompanying Statement is the responsibility of the Management of the promoter.The RERA Account considered for the purpose of issuing the certificate is as per details mentioned in the certificate, the provision for compliance with maintenance of RERA Account not validated while issuing the certificate.As informed to us by management, there is alteration in carpet area as compared to last return filed, we have appended new carpet areas provided to us by the management.The details mentioned in Annexure A such as carpet area, booking status, unit consideration, date of agreement to sale, encumbrance status, name, KYC and mobile numbers of allottees are as provided by the management. Received amount has been verified with the books of accounts.only Received amount grouped under "booking Deposit Recd" is considered.In case of sundry creditors of rajvee associates the amount paid is considered as towards basic amt only, hence total amt paid to them is considered as incurred and paid. .as informed to us by the management there was no stock in trade on the date of preparation of this certificate. Promoter has incurred cost but either invoices are not booked or invoices are not paid for  hence there is gap between cost incurred and incurred & paid.Promoter has received BU Permission for the project on 10/08/2020 vide certificate number  7783/271016/A7468/R0/M1.KYC details are taken as provided by the management we do not take responsibility of the same. the inventories are taken as provided by the management. in the BU Permission made available to us total units are 209 units wherein as per the filed 3A no of units are 223 as per the vikas parvangi however total built up area in sq mtr remains unchanged i.e 33061.76 in vikas parvangi as well as BU permission. moreover we have checked the date of number of vikas parvangi mentioned in BU. it pertains to 223 units. in the 3A uploaded with this certificate mistakenly the status of units are not changed from "Created" to " Released" Actually as on the date of certificate the mortgage loan in favour of the promoter has been paid in full and NOC for all the units are received which is updated as part of all NOC in form 1. however mistakenly the status has not been changed in form 3A filed by us.We have not verified the account other than RERA Account. We have not audited books of accounts of the promoter hence we have worked as per the data and details made available to us. due to technical error we had to generate udin multiple times and bank details once entered cannot be revised hence opening and closing is kept same
